New lists: asterisks, hash marks, and ";text:def" (wrong...)
* bullet
* l1
  * l2
  * l2
     * l3
 # one
 #two
 #three
Term1:
  definition1.1

  definition1.2
Term2 :
    definition2

    Term3:
      definition3
      Term4:
          definition4

          definition4.2
      Term5 :
        definition5

Mixed -
 * ul1
   # ul1-ol1
   # ul1-ol2
     * ul1-ol2-ul1
     * ul1-ol2-ul2
        * ul1-ol2-ul2-ul1
        * ul1-ol2-ul2-ul2

*  l1
   <pre>
      preformatted text
   </pre>
   * l2
----
